          "Absurdly formal 'usted' for friends",
          "'Establecimiento de ocio nocturno' instead of 'bar/disco'",
          "Sounds like a butler, not a friend",
          "Completely unnatural"
        ],
        "issues": ["formality_mismatch", "unnatural_phrasing", "wrong_vocabulary"],
        "what_to_improve": "Say '¿Quedamos?', '¿Salimos de fiesta?', use casual language"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bad_plans_002",
      "scenario": "plans",
      "prompt": "Accept an invitation to meet",
      "context": "Friend invites you for coffee",
      "response": {
        "text": "OK",
